      { q: 'Is FIRE realistic in India?', a: 'Yes. With lower cost of living outside metros, many Indians achieve FIRE with a corpus of ₹2–5 Crore.' },
      { q: 'What return should I assume for FIRE planning?', a: 'Use 10–12% for equity mutual funds, subtract 6–7% for inflation to get a real return of 4–6%.' }
